nodes.title: Added missing -B on `mvn` and build with native profile.
Added integration-test and fixed error on native build.
Changed JsonFormatter to use fresh StringBuilderWriter for every format
fix #111: avoiding thread unsafe access to StringBuilderWriter
update to use default branch from ecosystem
Added jacoco to get test coverage reports
Added support for disable output of the timestamp field.
Rename artifacts with the quarkus- prefix
Add support to flatten the MDC fields
Fixed issue where JsonProviders where optimized away by quarkus.
Added support for setting the zoneId, to use when formatting timestamp
Added support for providing custom JsonProviders using CDI.
Changed to use versions from parent.
docs: add SlyngDK as a contributor
Fixed import sorting and added impsort:check to build.yml
Added support for adding additional fields using the config.
Ignore the integration-test if performRelease is set
Changed to not run `integration-test` module on release
Changed skipNexusStagingDeployMojo from property to plugin
